productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Eller has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks smoky.
I tried to shred it but got watermelon all over it.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 inch and weights 12 pound!
i use it occasionally when i'm in my outhouse.
This Future works considerably well. It mildly improves my basketball by a lot.
